snippet.title: Kulebra and the Souls of Limbo - Kickstarter Relaunch Trailer (May 2022)
snippet.description:
A dead snake with a heart of gold embarks on a journey to find his purpose in a world where the same day plays on loop. Meet many colorful characters with their own daily schedule, help the residents of Limbo find peace by using your wits and detective skills to gather clues and items, and uncover the mystery of Limbo.

The demo for Kulebra and the Souls of Limbo is available for FREE!
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1678600/Kulebra_and_the_Souls_of_Limbo__Demo
Itch.io: https://gallagames.itch.io/kulebra-and-the-souls-of-limbo-demo

Kickstarter Relaunch (May 2022): https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/gallagames/kulebra-and-the-souls-of-limbo-relaunch
